FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]

    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]
ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

[olusturma_tarihi7], [t7].[rol] AS [rol0], [t7].[sifre_hash] AS [sifre_hash0], [t7].[telefon] AS [telefon3]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    INNER JOIN [tb_dukkan] AS [t0] ON [t].[dukkan_id] = [t0].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t1] ON [t].[musteri_id] = [t1].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t4] ON [t3].[kategori_id] = [t4].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t5] ON [t].[durum_id] = [t5].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t6] ON [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id] = [t6].[id]
    LEFT JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t7] ON [t].[atanan_kullanici_id] = [t7].[id]
    WHERE [t].[id] = @query_Id
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_notu] AS [t8]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t9] ON [t8].[kullanici_id] = [t9].[id]
) AS [s0] ON [s].[id] = [s0].[is_emri_id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t10].[id], [t10].[aciklama], [t10].[degisim_tarihi], [t10].[durum_id], [t10].[is_emri_id], [t10].[kullanici_id], [t10].[olusturma_tarihi], [t11].[id] AS [id0], [t11].[ad], [t11].[aktif], [t11].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t11].[renk], [t11].[sira], [t12].[id] AS [id1], [t12].[ad_soyad], [t12].[aktif] AS [aktif0], [t12].[dukkan_id], [t12].[email], [t12].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi1], [t12].[rol], [t12].[sifre_hash], [t12].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_durum_gecmisi] AS [t10]
    INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t11] ON [t10].[durum_id] = [t11].[id]

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]

    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    INNER JOIN [tb_dukkan] AS [t0] ON [t].[dukkan_id] = [t0].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t1] ON [t].[musteri_id] = [t1].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t4] ON [t3].[kategori_id] = [t4].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t5] ON [t].[durum_id] = [t5].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t6] ON [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id] = [t6].[id]
    LEFT JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t7] ON [t].[atanan_kullanici_id] = [t7].[id]
    WHERE [t].[id] = @query_Id
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_notu] AS [t8]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t9] ON [t8].[kullanici_id] = [t9].[id]
) AS [s0] ON [s].[id] = [s0].[is_emri_id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t10].[id], [t10].[aciklama], [t10].[degisim_tarihi], [t10].[durum_id], [t10].[is_emri_id], [t10].[kullanici_id], [t10].[olusturma_tarihi], [t11].[id] AS [id0], [t11].[ad], [t11].[aktif], [t11].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t11].[renk], [t11].[sira], [t12].[id] AS [id1], [t12].[ad_soyad], [t12].[aktif] AS [aktif0], [t12].[dukkan_id], [t12].[email], [t12].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi1], [t12].[rol], [t12].[sifre_hash], [t12].[telefon]

SELECT [t1].[id], [t1].[is_emri_no], [t1].[dukkan_id], [t1].[musteri_id], COALESCE([t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi], N''), [t0].[telefon], [t1].[cihaz_id], [t3].[marka] + N' ' + [t3].[model], [t2].[seri_no], [t1].[durum_id], [t4].[ad], [t4].[renk], [t1].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t1].[oncelik], [t1].[tahmini_ucret], [t1].[olusturma_tarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_ucret]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[dukkan_id] = @dukkanId
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t1]
INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t1].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t1].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t4] ON [t1].[durum_id] = [t4].[id]
ORDER BY [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

[s1].[dukkan_id], [s1].[email], [s1].[olusturma_tarihi1], [s1].[rol], [s1].[sifre_hash], [s1].[telefon]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [t].[id], [t].[ariza_aciklamasi], [t].[atanan_kullanici_id], [t].[cihaz_id], [t].[dukkan_id], [t].[durum_id], [t].[garanti_kapsaminda], [t].[is_emri_no], [t].[kesin_ucret], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[on_teshis], [t].[oncelik], [t].[tahmini_sure_gun], [t].[tahmini_ucret], [t].[tamamlanma_tarihi], [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id], [t].[teslim_tarihi], [t].[yapilan_islem], [t0].[id] AS [id0], [t0].[abonelik_bitis_tarihi], [t0].[ad], [t0].[adres], [t0].[aktif], [t0].[email], [t0].[firma_kodu], [t0].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t0].[telefon], [t0].[vergi_no], [t1].[id] AS [id1], [t1].[ad_soyad], [t1].[adres] AS [adres0], [t1].[email] AS [email0], [t1].[firma_adi], [t1].[musteri_tipi], [t1].[notlar], [t1].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi1], [t1].[telefon] AS [telefon0], [t1].[telefon2], [t1].[vergi_no] AS [vergi_no0], [t2].[id] AS [id2], [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id], [t2].[garanti_bitis_tarihi], [t2].[imei], [t2].[musteri_id] AS [musteri_id0], [t2].[notlar] AS [notlar0], [t2].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi2], [t2].[renk], [t2].[seri_no], [t3].[id] AS [id3], [t3].[aktif] AS [aktif0], [t3].[kategori_id], [t3].[marka], [t3].[model], [t3].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi3], [t4].[id] AS [id4], [t4].[ad] AS [ad0], [t4].[aktif] AS [aktif1], [t4].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi4], [t5].[id] AS [id5], [t5].[ad] AS [ad1], [t5].[aktif] AS [aktif2], [t5].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi5], [t5].[renk] AS [renk0], [t5].[sira], [t6].[id] AS [id6], [t6].[ad_soyad] AS [ad_soyad0], [t6].[aktif] AS [aktif3], [t6].[dukkan_id] AS [dukkan_id0], [t6].[email] AS [email1], [t6].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi6], [t6].[rol], [t6].[sifre_hash], [t6].[telefon] AS [telefon1], [t7].[id] AS [id7], [t7].[ad_soyad] AS [ad_soyad1], [t7].[aktif] AS [aktif4], [t7].[dukkan_id] AS [dukkan_id1], [t7].[email] AS [email2], [t7].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi7], [t7].[rol] AS [rol0], [t7].[sifre_hash] AS [sifre_hash0], [t7].[telefon] AS [telefon3]
    FROM [tb_is_emri] AS [t]
    INNER JOIN [tb_dukkan] AS [t0] ON [t].[dukkan_id] = [t0].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t1] ON [t].[musteri_id] = [t1].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz] AS [t2] ON [t].[cihaz_id] = [t2].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t3] ON [t2].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t3].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t4] ON [t3].[kategori_id] = [t4].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t5] ON [t].[durum_id] = [t5].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t6] ON [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id] = [t6].[id]
    LEFT JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t7] ON [t].[atanan_kullanici_id] = [t7].[id]
    WHERE [t].[id] = @query_Id
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_notu] AS [t8]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t9] ON [t8].[kullanici_id] = [t9].[id]
) AS [s0] ON [s].[id] = [s0].[is_emri_id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t10].[id], [t10].[aciklama], [t10].[degisim_tarihi], [t10].[durum_id], [t10].[is_emri_id], [t10].[kullanici_id], [t10].[olusturma_tarihi], [t11].[id] AS [id0], [t11].[ad], [t11].[aktif], [t11].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t11].[renk], [t11].[sira], [t12].[id] AS [id1], [t12].[ad_soyad], [t12].[aktif] AS [aktif0], [t12].[dukkan_id], [t12].[email], [t12].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi1], [t12].[rol], [t12].[sifre_hash], [t12].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_durum_gecmisi] AS [t10]
    INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t11] ON [t10].[durum_id] = [t11].[id]

SELECT [s].[id] AS [Id], [s].[musteri_id] AS [MusteriId], COALESCE([s].[ad_soyad], [s].[firma_adi], N'') AS [MusteriAd], [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] AS [CihazTanimId], [t3].[ad] AS [KategoriAd], [t2].[marka] AS [Marka], [t2].[model] AS [Model], [s].[seri_no] AS [SeriNo], [s].[imei] AS [Imei], [s].[renk] AS [Renk], [s].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [OlusturmaTarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[cihaz_tanim_id], [t].[imei], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[renk], [t].[seri_no], [t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi]

    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [tb_dukkan_musteri] AS [t1]
        WHERE [t0].[id] = [t1].[musteri_id] AND [t1].[dukkan_id] = @_currentUser_DukkanId)
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [s]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t2] ON [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t3] ON [t2].[kategori_id] = [t3].[id]
ORDER BY [s].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

2026-01-03 11:32:26.017 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@_currentUser_DukkanId='?' (DbType = Guid), @p='?' (DbType = Int32), @p0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s].[id] AS [Id], [s].[musteri_id] AS [MusteriId], COALESCE([s].[ad_soyad], [s].[firma_adi], N'') AS [MusteriAd], [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] AS [CihazTanimId], [t3].[ad] AS [KategoriAd], [t2].[marka] AS [Marka], [t2].[model] AS [Model], [s].[seri_no] AS [SeriNo], [s].[imei] AS [Imei], [s].[renk] AS [Renk], [s].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [OlusturmaTarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[cihaz_tanim_id], [t].[imei], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[renk], [t].[seri_no], [t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi]
    FROM [tb_cihaz] AS [t]
    INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [tb_dukkan_musteri] AS [t1]
        WHERE [t0].[id] = [t1].[musteri_id] AND [t1].[dukkan_id] = @_currentUser_DukkanId)
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [s]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t2] ON [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t3] ON [t2].[kategori_id] = [t3].[id]
ORDER BY [s].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

    SELECT 1

2026-01-03 15:42:58.390 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (21ms) [Parameters=[@_currentUser_DukkanId='?' (DbType = Guid), @p='?' (DbType = Int32), @p0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [s].[id] AS [Id], [s].[musteri_id] AS [MusteriId], COALESCE([s].[ad_soyad], [s].[firma_adi], N'') AS [MusteriAd], [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] AS [CihazTanimId], [t3].[ad] AS [KategoriAd], [t2].[marka] AS [Marka], [t2].[model] AS [Model], [s].[seri_no] AS [SeriNo], [s].[imei] AS [Imei], [s].[renk] AS [Renk], [s].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [OlusturmaTarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[cihaz_tanim_id], [t].[imei], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[renk], [t].[seri_no], [t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi]
    FROM [tb_cihaz] AS [t]
    INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [tb_dukkan_musteri] AS [t1]
        WHERE [t0].[id] = [t1].[musteri_id] AND [t1].[dukkan_id] = @_currentUser_DukkanId)
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [s]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t2] ON [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t3] ON [t2].[kategori_id] = [t3].[id]
ORDER BY [s].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC

FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[cihaz_tanim_id], [t].[imei], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[renk], [t].[seri_no], [t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi]

    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY

    INNER JOIN [tb_is_durumu] AS [t5] ON [t].[durum_id] = [t5].[id]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t6] ON [t].[teslim_alan_kullanici_id] = [t6].[id]
    LEFT JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t7] ON [t].[atanan_kullanici_id] = [t7].[id]
    WHERE [t].[id] = @query_Id
) AS [s]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t8].[id], [t8].[is_emri_id], [t8].[kullanici_id], [t8].[not_metni], [t8].[olusturma_tarihi], [t9].[id] AS [id0], [t9].[ad_soyad], [t9].[aktif], [t9].[dukkan_id], [t9].[email], [t9].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [olusturma_tarihi0], [t9].[rol], [t9].[sifre_hash], [t9].[telefon]
    FROM [tb_is_notu] AS [t8]
    INNER JOIN [tb_kullanici] AS [t9] ON [t8].[kullanici_id] = [t9].[id]

SELECT [s].[id] AS [Id], [s].[musteri_id] AS [MusteriId], COALESCE([s].[ad_soyad], [s].[firma_adi], N'') AS [MusteriAd], [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] AS [CihazTanimId], [t3].[ad] AS [KategoriAd], [t2].[marka] AS [Marka], [t2].[model] AS [Model], [s].[seri_no] AS [SeriNo], [s].[imei] AS [Imei], [s].[renk] AS [Renk], [s].[olusturma_tarihi] AS [OlusturmaTarihi]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[id], [t].[cihaz_tanim_id], [t].[imei], [t].[musteri_id], [t].[olusturma_tarihi], [t].[renk], [t].[seri_no], [t0].[ad_soyad], [t0].[firma_adi]
    FROM [tb_cihaz] AS [t]
    INNER JOIN [tb_musteri] AS [t0] ON [t].[musteri_id] = [t0].[id]
    WHERE EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [tb_dukkan_musteri] AS [t1]
        WHERE [t0].[id] = [t1].[musteri_id] AND [t1].[dukkan_id] = @_currentUser_DukkanId)
    ORDER BY [t].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
    OFFSET @p ROWS FETCH NEXT @p0 ROWS ONLY
) AS [s]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_tanim] AS [t2] ON [s].[cihaz_tanim_id] = [t2].[id]
INNER JOIN [tb_cihaz_kategori] AS [t3] ON [t2].[kategori_id] = [t3].[id]
ORDER BY [s].[olusturma_tarihi] DESC
